<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{title}} - Deno App</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <nav id="main-nav">
      <a href="/" id="nav-home">Home</a>
      <a href="/about" id="nav-about">About</a>
      <div class="dropdown">
        <a href="#" class="dropbtn" id="nav-resources">Resources â–¼</a>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
          <a href="/resources/documentation" id="nav-resources-docs">Documentation</a>
          <a href="/resources/tutorials" id="nav-resources-tutorials">Tutorials</a>
          <a href="/resources/support" id="nav-resources-support">Support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{#if isAdmin}}
        <a href="/admin/users" id="nav-admin-users">Users</a>
        <a href="/admin/roles" id="nav-admin-roles">Roles</a>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if isLoggedIn}}
        <a href="/logout" class="nav-right" id="nav-logout">Logout</a>
      {{else}}
        <a href="/login" class="nav-right" id="nav-login">Login</a>
      {{/if}}
    </nav>
    
    {{#if isLoggedIn}}
      <div class="user-info" id="user-info-display">Logged in as: {{user.email}}</div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <h1 id="page-title">{{title}}</h1>
    
    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Application Documentation</h2>
      <p>Welcome to the comprehensive documentation for the Deno web application.</p>
      
      <div class="doc-section">
        <h3>Getting Started</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Installation:</strong> Follow the setup instructions in the README</li>
          <li><strong>Configuration:</strong> Set up your database and environment variables</li>
          <li><strong>First Steps:</strong> Create your first user and explore the interface</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="doc-section">
        <h3>User Management</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Creating Users:</strong> Admin users can create new accounts with various roles</li>
          <li><strong>Role Assignment:</strong> Users can have multiple roles (admin, user, editor, viewer)</li>
          <li><strong>Password Security:</strong> All passwords are hashed using bcrypt with 12 rounds</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="doc-section">
        <h3>Role Management</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Creating Roles:</strong> Define custom roles with descriptions</li>
          <li><strong>Assigning Roles:</strong> Assign multiple roles to users</li>
          <li><strong>Role Protection:</strong> Cannot delete roles that are assigned to users</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="doc-section">
        <h3>API Reference</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>GET /api/data:</strong> Returns current timestamp</li>
          <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Session-based authentication with cookies</li>
          <li><strong>Admin Routes:</strong> Protected routes requiring admin role</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
